[00:00.000]作曲 : Charlton Howard/Kbeazy
[00:00.000][by:stillworkingonit]
[00:13.546]Who was I to think that I could fix you, baby?
[00:13.546]我怎敢妄想叫你回心转意 亲爱的
[00:16.709]Who would I be if I didn't miss you, baby?
[00:16.709]若不曾失去你 我又会是怎样 亲爱的
[00:19.944]I hope that you know you were appreciated
[00:19.944]愿你明白 你始终被我捧在手心
[00:22.458]Around my house I still got up all of our pictures, baby
[00:22.458]家里依旧存着我们的合照 亲爱的
[00:25.548]Mmm
[00:25.548]Mmm
[00:26.426]'Cause I still love you, that's how I feel at my core
[00:26.426]因为我依然爱着你 这是我心底最真的感受
[00:29.591]Flew different states to come see you in-between tour
